Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The attacks by the Gundams\Nsent by the Space Colonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.49,0:01:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...reflected the colonies'\Nretaliatory intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ has masked its identity\Nin the Alliance Military...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the Gundams' missions\Nis to attack them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The year is After Colony 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ has finally taken center stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,With an army of elite soldiers\Nat his command...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...Treize Khushrenada has begun to\Nwipe out the Alliance Military.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle between OZ and the\Nmobile suits sent to Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...causes serious repercussions\Non the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.26,0:02:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you now, Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got a 10 percent\Nchance of succeeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But he can do it for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a miserable mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I totally screwed up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the Lightning Count,\Nwe saved the beautiful town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Alliance is probably\Nregrouping their force...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...after the surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use this base as our\Nheadquarters for future fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The beauty of these towns\Ndoesn't change with rulers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Noin...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ's objective isn't to rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to free countries from\Nthe stranglehold...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.97,0:02:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the United Earth\NSphere Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be unnatural\Ncoming from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:03:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I believe OZ should\Nbe given due respect...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...for giving a second chance\Nto those countries...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...which formed the Alliance\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The mobile suit carrier from\NVictoria Base is arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Otto, I'm so glad to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here now, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Otto shouldn't\Neven be standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,His ribs are broken, and\Nhe has internal injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Zechs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This Tallgeese you've been\Nwaiting for is one vicious suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the Tallgeese...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like a thing that\Nwas scrapped 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The revolution speed\Napplied by the verniers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...allows it to reach more than\Nthree times that of the Aries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But we were unable to\Ndetermine its maximum speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I passed out during the trials.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the test pilot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tallgeese can't be\Ncontrolled by just anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Zechs is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you overrating my skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I trust in your abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be using this right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him to the medical room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Noin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the mobile suit troops\Nready to leave at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go to the Alliance's\NSanc Kingdom base.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sanc Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're freeing them\Nfrom the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Any objections to this mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going on this Tallgeese.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Without even a test ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be taking it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to stake my\Nchances on this mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanc Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs' homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice shot, Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome! Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wave back or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cheering for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:05:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is where you went.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's pretty smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Changing schools when\Nyou've gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's natural for people our age\Nto be in school, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to act normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be as suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you acted natural instead\Nof being so secretive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just chill out\Nand have fun as a student?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And stay outta my way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us are going after\Nthe same thing, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hide it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it in your eyes\Nas plain as day, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the first one to\Ndestroy that fortress wins?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found you, Heero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero. I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not typical, wanting to\Nsee the guy trying to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Three mobile suit carriers and\Nseven escort planes approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirmed as OZ troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the OZ troops\Ntrying to pull here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They've released the suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the assault centralized.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need to take over\Nthe main facilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Following OZ's coup d'état...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...the United Earth Sphere\NAlliance Military...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...enters a state of confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Alliance Military soldiers remain\Nconfined in their bases...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...without an understanding of\Nwhat in fact is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The United Earth Sphere\NAlliance was initially formed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...to handle disputes between\Nthe countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But with its expansion in\Nmilitary power, the Alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...soon took over governments\Nwith militaristic control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ is now planning to\Nfree the many countries...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...that were forced into the\NAlliance in this manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But the increase in the\NAlliance's military power...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...was a direct result of the\Nmobile suits provided by OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, many countries\Nquestioned OZ's activities...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...noting that after the coup\Nd'état, military control...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...would continue and conditions\Nwould remain the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All mobile suits have left{\i0}\N{\i1}the carriers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll leave as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be backing you up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Concentrate only on achieving{\i0}\N{\i1}your mission, Lieutenant Zechs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm totally focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll lure away ground troops,{\i0}\N{\i1}but some might fly toward you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If our data 's right, I should{\i0}\N{\i1}be able to outrun them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good luck!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The mobility of this heavy suit\Ndepends on the vernier output.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to take\Na lot of effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't falter now with\Nthe Sanc Kingdom before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Take over the runway on\Nthe east side!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This speed is deadly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I could get away by\Nincreasing the output.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I hesitating?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Transmission from OZ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Disarm your weapons{\i0}\N{\i1}and surrender!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have no wish to{\i0}\N{\i1}continue this battle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the ones that attacked,\Nso you should be retreating!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Standby to fire laser beams!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Headquarters didn't mention\Nthose lasers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned laser beams!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Noin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Order all units to withdraw{\i0}\N{\i1}at once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea they had\Nthis much firepower...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...but we're still in the fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We should leave for now\Nand regroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll withdraw to where\Nwe landed the carriers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I acting like\Nsuch a coward?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I could defeat them with\Nthis Tallgeese.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I could ignore the lasers\Nand destroy their headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've mastered many mobile suits\Nin the past, so what gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I afraid of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll die if I keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This mobile suit is capable\Nof defeating any enemy it faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But it does have one weak point;\Nthe pilot is a human being!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady, won't you join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Treize, what would you\Nsuggest for our next target?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just continue fighting\Nand winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean we should\Nconquer the Earth Sphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then OZ would then be hated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd become a target\Nfor the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Treize...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Those that are hated must\Nremain strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be the perfect\Nmotivation for OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Quatre, if anything\Nwere to happen to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...how would we explain it\Nto your father in the colony?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have confidence\Nin us, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Our sole purpose here\Nis to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Quatre!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But Captain Rashid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Quatre has promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...that he won't leave on\Nhis own any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, there's no time\Nto stand around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Load up the weapons on\Nyour mobile suits or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Rashid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm upset with you too;\Ndon't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There were five suits in all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure they're\Nall called Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all Gundams?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They're violent and dangerous\Nbut they're all nice guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be sure of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The soul of outer space\Ntells me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The soul of outer space?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The soul of outer space...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You call that fun,\Njust sitting there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't said a word\Nfor two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd be doing\Nyou a favor bringing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat it up before it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it here\Nso help yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And clean the dishes\Nafter you're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta learn your manners\Nwhile you're still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess quiet people\Nattract quiet friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Might not be the best java.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no right\Npiloting the Nataku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pulse has now\Nstabilized...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...but there are irregularities\Nin the circulatory system.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean I should just\Nbe glad to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs, what in the\Nworld happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I really underestimated\Nthe Tallgeese.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:15:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It completely ignores\Nthe pilot's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It has an audacious design...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...that far exceeds today's\Nmost advanced equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It ignores the pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes into consideration\Nall types of battle patterns...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...and makes it possible\Nfor the one suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...to achieve victory\Non its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,At least that's how\NI found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've become such\Na coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The more I try to utilize\Nthe mobile suit's abilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...the more I start doubting\Nmy own abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I start asking myself, "is that\Nall you're capable of doing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than a suit for battle,\Nit's a suit for dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a brave pilot to\Nbring out its true potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A brave pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Brave enough to risk\Ndeath for victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have a long way to\Ngo to conquer my own fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I've got to get back\Nto the Sanc Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Any normal person would've\Nbeen dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:16:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving, but you have to\Nstay here and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, but not on the Tallgeese.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Noin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tallgeese is essential\Nto us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm positive its design\Nis the same as the Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As I told you, I believe\Nthe Gundams inherited...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...the reckless design of\Nthe Tallgeese.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The mobile suits' origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's crucial for\Nme to pilot the Tallgeese...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...to defeat the Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tallgeese is for suicide\Nmissions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I understand what\Nthe Gundams are up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They're searching for a place\Nsuitable for their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's very difficult\Nfor you to lie still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...with the Sanc Kingdom close\Nby, but you must do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll attack tomorrow evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Tomorrow evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Tallgeese has taken off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What're you doing?!{\i0}\N{\i1}Return immediately!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This Tallgeese should\Nbe able to take over...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Sanc Kingdom's\Nheadquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I should know I understand\Nthe Tallgeese's strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be honored to sacrifice\Nmy life for you, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow me to assist\Nin fulfilling your dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do this for you\NLieutenant Zechs, not for OZ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Otto...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I will attain victory in\Nreturn for my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not making sense Otto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Return at once! Otto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:18:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come all the way here\Njust to chase after a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you surprised, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't help myself;\NI wanted to see him so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you understand\Nhow I feel, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to have Heero's\Nsupport...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...until I overcome\Nmy sadness over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But he keeps running\Nfrom me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I got here first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What took you, Heero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I left\Nyou some action!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how long\NI can stand this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I'd been able to\Npilot the Tallgeese...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...this never would\Nhave happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The new type of mobile suit\Nis approaching fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Direct all laser beams\Nat that suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,LONG LIVE KING ZECHS!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Otto...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It took me 13 years to\Nreturn to these grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been much bloodshed\Nalong the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I've only been able\Nto live a lifestyle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...that counters your\Npacifist teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My hands are too stained\Nwith blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely unfit to head\Nthe Peacecraft monarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure she would\Nbe able to head the country...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...as you'd intended.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight to make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've failed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was attacked!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Think the colonies did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, good looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty nice day today, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta get to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me stay by you\Na little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna be stronger,\Njust like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Battles that risk lives\Nonly produce mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what meaning does\NOtto's death have?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Une announces\Na plan to transport Tauruses...
